  <entry>
    <title>20220728</title>
    <link href="https://kyoukawa.github.io/2022/07/29/20220728/"/>
    <id>https://kyoukawa.github.io/2022/07/29/20220728/</id>
    <published>2022-07-28T22:37:39.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-07-29T00:17:30.769Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="字典树-Trie"><a href="#字典树-Trie" class="headerlink" title="字典树(Trie)"></a>字典树(Trie)</h1><h2 id="引出问题"><a href="#引出问题" class="headerlink" title="引出问题"></a>引出问题</h2><blockquote><p>如果你经常上网冲浪,在搜索时会发现有一个建议功能.<br><img src="/pic/20220728/DuckDuckGo.png" alt="DuckDuckGo的搜索建议功能"><br>那么这是怎么实现的呢?</p></blockquote><h2 id="前置知识"><a href="#前置知识" class="headerlink" title="前置知识"></a>前置知识</h2><p>首先我们要了解什么是字符串的前缀</p><h3 id="前缀"><a href="#前缀" class="headerlink" title="前缀"></a>前缀</h3><p>假设有一个字符串“ABC”<br>我们称“A”,”AB”.”ABC”为它的前缀.</p><p>所以为了好研究,我们把问题简化成给定一个字符串,找出数据中所有以这个串为前缀的字符串.</p><h2 id="算法设计"><a href="#算法设计" class="headerlink" title="算法设计"></a>算法设计</h2><p>假设数据中有<strong>n</strong>个字符串,最长为<strong>m</strong>,有<strong>k</strong>种字符</p><h3 id="暴力"><a href="#暴力" class="headerlink" title="暴力"></a>暴力</h3><p><del>一个判断前缀有什么难的,我直接暴力循环</del></p><p>如果是直接循环,那么单次查询的时间复杂度将是O(nm)</p><p>所以暴力肯定行不通:(</p><h3 id="字典树"><a href="#字典树" class="headerlink" title="字典树"></a>字典树</h3><h4 id="建树"><a href="#建树" class="headerlink" title="建树"></a>建树</h4><p>建一个树,每个节点都是一个字符串,根为空串.<br>每个节点的孩子都是这个节点添加一个字符.</p><p>就像这样(在iPad上用手画的,有亿点丑)<br><img src="/pic/20220728/%E5%BB%BA%E6%A0%91.png" alt="建树"></p><p>这样的话,节点数量就是<strong>nm</strong>,但是时间复杂度减少了.<br>建树每次插入,需要遍历到插入的字符串的每个前缀,所以复杂度<strong>O(m)</strong><br>所以建树总复杂度为<strong>O(nm)</strong></p><h4 id="查询"><a href="#查询" class="headerlink" title="查询"></a>查询</h4><p>单次查询的复杂度则降低到了<strong>O(m)</strong><br>比暴力少了不少:)</p><h4 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h4><h5 id="定义"><a href="#定义" class="headerlink" title="定义"></a>定义</h5><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> n,m,tot=<span class="number">1</span>; <span class="comment">//n个字符串,m次查询,tot表示当前节点数量</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> tr[maxn][<span class="number">26</span>]; <span class="comment">//tr[i][j]表示第i个节点添加第j种字符后到达哪个节点,第二维即k</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> ed[maxn]; <span class="comment">//ed[i]表示以i号节点表示的字符串在数据中的数量</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="建树-1"><a href="#建树-1" class="headerlink" title="建树"></a>建树</h5><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">Insert</span><span class="params">(string str)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> cur=<span class="number">1</span>; <span class="comment">//上次到达节点的下标</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">char</span> ch: str)&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//循环每个字符</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (tr[cur][ch-<span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>]==<span class="number">0</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//如果这个节点不存在</span></span><br><span class="line">            tr[cur][ch-<span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>]=++tot; <span class="comment">//创建新节点,节点数量+1</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        cur=tr[cur][ch-<span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>]; <span class="comment">//保存当前下标</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    ed[cur]++; <span class="comment">//插入结束</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="查询-1"><a href="#查询-1" class="headerlink" title="查询"></a>查询</h5><p>例如计算一个串在数据中所有的前缀的数量</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">Find</span><span class="params">(string str)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> cur=<span class="number">1</span>,cnt=<span class="number">0</span>; <span class="comment">//cnt用来记录数量</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">char</span> ch: str)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(ed[cur])&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        cnt+=ed[cur];</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        cur=tr[cur][ch-<span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>];</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(ed[cur]) cnt+=ed[cur];</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> cnt;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>可以发现大体上与建树的代码一致</p><p>快去试一试<a href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/P8306">luogu模版题</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
